    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162850/extras/c2b12a943b8b929fea353e8e335a2d3b.avif?t=1763244608\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162850/extras_big/c2b12a943b8b929fea353e8e335a2d3b.avif?t=1763244608 width=800 height=291 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lightning Katana is a fast-paced action FPS with hype parries, and even hyper combos inspired by the likes of Hotline Miami, Doom Classic, Katana Zero, and Devil May Cry. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slash, Parry, Shoot and Dodge Roll your way through the Neo-Nippon Yakuza to avenge your pet Dogsuke and take on the top brass and baddest hit squad in all of Neo Nippon, the <i>Ryujin Ichizoku</i>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162850/extras/483512e6ca467f4e86fba9f9696958af.poster.avif?t=1763244608\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162850/extras/483512e6ca467f4e86fba9f9696958af.webm?t=1763244608\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162850/extras/483512e6ca467f4e86fba9f9696958af.mp4?t=1763244608\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Featuring:</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lightning Fast Fury</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Always be moving with quick dodge rolls and perfect parries to slash your way through the Neo-Yakuza stronghold. Hesitation can mean death, and you go down almost as fast as your enemies, so be careful as a well placed parry is the only way to recover health. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flashy Elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat empowered enemies to temporarily gain their abilities. Shoot a powerful lightning bolt that fries anything in its path, or ride the winds of Fujin to slice through any yakuza that stand in your way. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SSStylish Combos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chain together kills to earn S, SS and P ranks in each level and earn Schmunny to buy new levels, or try your hand at Gauntlet Mode to earn Bones for some decorations in the Hub.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plenty of ways to Slice and Dice</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is hand-crafted with a different mechanic or idea in mind, be it slicing through as fast as you can with an array of well timed abilities, or kicking molotovs into your enemies' faces. See if you can master them all for the illustrious P-Rank!</p>",
